				<h3>The Schedule</h3>
				<p><strong>On Friday April 8th:</strong> Check-in will start at <strong>6:30pm</strong>, and we'll host the opening ceremony at <strong>9pm</strong>. Coding begins at <strong>10pm</strong>.</p>
